{"tid":407850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯：只說了「無赦」不會道歉","createTime":"2017-09-20T17:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T03:28:56.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":347,"uniUserReply":135,"replies":[{"pid":"a4f27d8bf89c06144165849bee2252cb060ba9ca","tid":407850,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/LSD.PETITION.2000.2009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FLSD.PETITION.2000.2009.jpg&h=9afbaa6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】「殺無赦」的言論引起爭議，立法會議員何君堯再次解釋，他說只說了「無赦」，不擔心會受檢控，不會收回言論也不會道歉，強調言論不涉煽動他人犯法。有團體就遊行到律師會，要求革除何君堯的律師資格。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯再解釋「殺無赦」言論，他說當日是附和屏山鄉事委員會主席曾樹和，他只是說了「無赦」，無意煽動他人犯法，不收回言論也不會道歉。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯不擔心會受到檢控，又說近日面對網上的語言暴力，與家人受到網上欺凌，會向警方舉報。<br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超表示，已收到市民報案，強調言論自由有限制。<br />\n<br />\n而社民連、人民力量等約四十人遊行到香港律師會總部，促請律師會紀律聆訊小組跟進，並革除何君堯的律師資格。律師會派代表接信，隨後透過新聞稿指，會按既定程序處理投訴，暫不評論個別個案。<br />\n<br />\n＃要聞<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/qtknlhq21/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fqtknlhq21%2Fimage.jpg&h=07c4a87e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29305f712ff11b02ba32f6daa6bc924a5588131b","tid":407850,"uid":48139,"like":199,"dislike":0,"score":199,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T18:01:20.000Z","msg":"淆底獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3446513834bb886099aac4c6aca185a64600155","tid":407850,"uid":4519,"like":162,"dislike":3,"score":159,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T18:02:13.000Z","msg":"全港市民曼德拉效應？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36975af03be5be8a39536ec464c3ecbbc54b7d7","tid":407850,"uid":57226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T18:04:24.000Z","msg"